About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise.

All the films of the Spy Universe are blockbusters with Pathaan being the all-time highest grossing Hindi film ever. The YRF Spy Universe is now one of the biggest IP’s in the history of Indian cinema. The next film from this franchise is Tiger 3 releasing this Diwali!

YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime:

Pankaj and Shreya meet a scientist in the jungle who is trapped on the Island. The Tribal People of the Island agreed to help ACP Pradyuman and his team. Abhijeet and Tarika rush to the Island to save their team. Will Team CID find out the truth? To know more, watch this thrilling episode of CID.

Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1006
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch more clips:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIXlaVRYtJLG6YjpiV0UjUnY

Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: Takeshi’s Castle - Date Announcement | @BBKiVines | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
That wasn’t very professional of them (we’re just happy it's happening) 🤪
Takeshi’s Castle ft. #BhuvanOnPrime, Nov 2

About Prime Video: Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies & TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place. Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ₹1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

snippet.title: MUTTON CHOPS FRY | Mutton Bone Fry Cooking and Eating | Mutton Chops Recipe Cooking in Village
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook tasty mutton chops fry recipe using traditional ingredients. Mutton chops are the one type of bones with meat in lamb. We get mutton chops from 16 lambs, and the remaining parts of the goat are cooked as mutton gravy.

In the evening, we taste the fried mutton chops with our favorite mutton gravy!

snippet.title: Aspirants and @PleaseSitDown mock interview with @AnubhavSinghBassi | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
We didn't know that we needed to see Vijendar Chauhan and Bassi on the same screen until now
#AspirantsOnPrime , new season, 25th Oct

About Prime Video: Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies & TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place. Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ₹1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3912 | 26 Oct 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3912: Artists Kaha Hai?
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu Sena has made elaborate preparations for the Golkuldham Garba celebration. They have devised a one-of-a-kind manner to greet each and every Gokuldham inhabitant. Tapu Sena had written a little poem for every one of them based on their personality traits. Sodhi is presented as the most lively character, whilst Popatlal is recognized for his sweet and endearing manner. Jetha's verse is about his store, and it makes him happy. Later, the artist gang shows up late, which causes everyone to panic.
 
Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3912, 26 Oct 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Jab insaan ke paas khone ke liye kuch nahi hota to paane ke liye poori duniya hoti hai. Shiv ab ye samajh chuka hai ki usse kamar kas kar mehnat karni hi hogi kyunki uska ghar kafi peeche chhot gaya hai. SSC sir ke star student number one rank to le aata hai lekin usse Khanna ko bech deta hai. Idhar iss dhokhe ke baad SSC apni life ki sabse badi ladayi ke liye tayyar ho raha hai to udhar Shiv depression ke kale badal se ghir chuka hai. Kya nayi hope ka suraj phir niklega?

official Music video🔥🔥💯🪬🚷
Taiyaar Raho Kattar Fam 🏃🏻

The most awaited music video for the hood anthem that continues to create waves is finally here !!

Singe / Performer: MC Stan ( Official baap )
Music Composer: MC Stan 
Author / Lyrics: MC Stan
Prod. by MC STΔN



  LYRICS :   
              
                      “ HOOK “

Chodna kam chillana jyada , Mein basti ka hasti 
mein malum kya kider se aata ,  P town baby 
Mein tumlog ko accha seekharela , bhai aane do peti
Yeh lund k bal , mere samne banra braZy

Mein basti ka , hasti bro 
Agyele bhai log , abhi kalti lo
Maine bombay mei bachaya ek , bacchi ko
Ider fire hogayeli dekh , palti bro

Mein basti ka , hasti broo
Amir mein hogayela , gareeb hai flow
Represent karta mein , basti ko
Yeh bhadwe karele nakli , show

                 ( VERSE - 1 )

Mein rapper nai , gangster hai 
Tu rapper nai , dancer hai
Acting tu karela rawas ha par , tu shyad se actor hai
Mein janeka  , dost log k matter mei 

Teku Marneka maan bhi nai karela  , sadela cancer hai tu 
Teko isleye mei leke nai jata bro kider bhi , kyuki bro phachad hai tu 

Yeh shemde ku batare ,
Apun kider se aare ann kider ko jaare 
Yeh basti mei pakare ,
Yeh lund k baal ku , lund pr mare

Aaj stannyy bole phakat hai ,
Leke jayega teku , mein bhaga k 
Tere baju wale , mere gaane bajate
Meko malum na , ed kaise bhagate
 phakat hai !

Mein actor ka ladka nai , aayela mei basti se 
meko bolte basti ka hasti
Mein gareebi se aayela bro , bombae ki public meko bolneki jande bacchi

Mere gaano pe , agar haat nai varti
Mere shows pe nai , badach ki gardi
Meri malum na , kider pan chalti 
Mere dost log ki gand, kaiku jaltiiiiiiiiiiiii ?

                      “ HOOK “

Chodna kam chillana jyada , Mein basti ka hasti 
mein malum kya kider se aata , P town baby

Mein basti ka , hasti broo

Represent karta mein , basti ko
Yeh bhadwe karele nakli , show

               ( VERSE  - 2 )

Maine Bola khudko , altaf shaikh 
Tu tera dekh , wer is ma shades 
Wer is ma js , now these days
uh heard ma name , fuck dat fame 
use ur brain , stay in ur lane
Apun dono same
Nobody knows ma , pain 
Mein bolrela sach , mere sach se bach

Mein bolrela hindi ( Hindi )
Meri shawty jab , lagati bindi 
Meko goli nai , khaneka neend ki
Mein club mei jab , karela entry

Jaise saxxhi mei , horeli entry
Mein jhaad pe kabhi , chatda nai panchi 
Tera 3 din jalayega , one piece 
Maine ghar dikhaya , woch meri galti

Tune chowki mei , kha dali palti

Tumko gand dhone aaneki nai ,  tabhi se karra mein rap

Mera vishye , no cap

Phele mere tak , poch

Aai jhaun tak mitra mandal bro

snippet.title: #Video - छम्मा छम्मा | Shilpi Raj | Namrita Malla | Bhojpuri Hot Song | Shilpi Raj New Song 2023
snippet.description:
नम्रिता मल्ला के शानदार नृत्य और शिल्पी राज की आवाज में नए भोजपुरी गाने "छम्मा छम्मा" का आनंद लें! इस धमाकेदार गाने का आनंद ले।

इस नए भोजपुरी गान का मज़ा लेते रहिये और हमारे चैनल को सब्सक्राइब करके टिप्स भोजपुरी के साथ जुड़े रहिये.
https://www.youtube.com/tipsBhojpuri

Song Credits:
Song Name : Chamma Chamma
Singer : Shilpi Raj
Lyricist : Ajit Mandal
Music : Arya Sharma
Studio : Shivay Studio Delhi
Recordist : Abhishekh

Original Song Credits:
Music : Anu Malik
Lyrics : Sameer

Video Credits:
Video by : Krishna Amrit films
Featuring : Namrita Malla
Director : Lakkie Vishwakarma
Choreographer : Lakkie Vishwakarma
DOP : Yogesh Singh
Assistant Choreographer : Suresh, Ashu, Binod
DI : Rohit

Special Thanks : Ajit Mandal,Rocky Raja, Suraj Katoch

For Movie & Album Please Get in Touch with:
Mr. Vijay Kashyap - +91 98100 34523 - vijayk@tips.in

Lyrics:

मुखड़ा:
बानी खाब के रानी हमर लाख कहानी
देखी हमरा बढे सबके परेशानी
चाहे बनाबल सभे दिल जनीया ।।
छम्मा छम्मा बाजेरे मेरी पैजनीया

अंतरा १:
हमरा नखडा पे होत बहुते खर्चा बा ।
अबत सारा शहर मे हमरे चर्चा बा ।।
हम हुस्न के मलिका हई हमर ना कवनो जोर बा  ।
गाव गाव और गली गली मे हमरे नाम के शोर बा ।।
पागल बनाबे चेहरा के पनीया ।।

अंतरा २:
केहु पारो कहेला केहु कहे छविली
केहु कह के बोलाबेला हमके नशीली।
पुलीस दरोगा सभे लोग ठुमका के हमरा फैन बा।
सज सबर के घर से निकलल हमरा खातिर बैन बा ।।
कहीया बनब केकर दुल्हनिया
छमा छमा।।

snippet.title: एक Autodriver ने क्यों तान दी Freddy पर बंदूक? | CID | Haunted | 26 Oct 2023 | Full Episode
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

A haunting incident takes place with two men, as soon as they entered inside a strange house. Now, Stay Tuned to know how will CID officers investigate about the case and get the hidden facts about the whole incident.

Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1180
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch all Haunted episodes of CID:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIW-fswW2LsXDIZWZqFRLWUF

Kitne arso se tumhaara hi mujhe
Intezar hai

Ooh Ooh x4

Tum jo paas aayi chumne ka yun bahaana leke
Tabse tum meri ho dastaan

Chaand ko bulaakar tumne chamkaayi meri jo raatein
Tabse main tumahara hi hua

Dono hi kalaiyon pe chaandi hai saji
Hothon pe jo laali hai dil mein bas gayi

Yeh milan kaisi, aag hai
Jal jaane ki hi, aas hai
Madhoshi ho ya nah bhi ho
Is pyaar ki gehraayi ka koi
Inteha nahi

Ooh Ooh x2

Naachne ka mann kare toh, jhoom lenge hum
Aur sitaaron ke bageechey, ghoom lenge hum

Thodi si mazaakiya bhi baatein hum karenge
Mil gaya hai aashiayaan hum aakhon se kahenge

Yun hota hai pyaar kyun
Thoda dar bhi hai, thoda junoon

Hai gavah, mehlif ki betabi
Jane kaise koi keh sake ki yeh
Itefaaq hai

Ooh Ooh x2

Yeh kaisi mulaqat hai
Jaise sadiyon se tum meri jaan ho
Ab kaise, main yeh samjhaaun
Kitne arso se Tumhaara hi mujhe 
intezar hai

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3911 | 25 Oct 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3911: Bina Budget Ki Navratri
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide proclaims that there will be no Garba this year because of a lack of cash. After learning about Bhide's choice, everyone is saddened. Residents of Gokuldham suggest financial ideas for the society, but Bhide decrees that each gift must be up to five thousand. After hearing Bhide's statements, the Gokuldham residents grew reluctant once more. Tapu Sena comes and discusses the sponsorship they have acquired. Gokuldham Society has a great opportunity to get their well-known Garba sponsored.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3911, 25 Oct 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3910 | 24 Oct 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3910: Sabse Pehele Aya Jethalal
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha arrives early to the clubhouse for the Navaratri meeting because Bhide has told him that he will fail to reach on time. Jetha hides himself so that no one notices that he has arrived ahead of everyone else. After a while, Bhide and Madhavi come, and Bhide informs Madhavi that Jetha has broken his promise. Taarak stands beside his friend Jetha and notifies Bhide that Jetha will be arriving soon. Iyer believes Jetha will be late as well, but Babita believes Jetha will not be late this time. Bhide closes the clubhouse door, and everyone is astonished to hear Jetha's voice as soon as he begins speaking.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3910, 24 Oct 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

मेघनाद की मृत्यु से क्रोधित हो रावण स्वयं रणभूमि में उतरता है। देवतागण पैदल नंगे पाव राम देख भगवान ब्रह्मा जी के सुझाव पर इन्द्र का सारथी मातलि को दिव्य रथ के साथ राम के पास भेजते है। रावण राम को इन्द्र के रथ पर आरूढ़ देखकर परेशान हो जाता है। राम रावण के बीच भयंकर युद्ध होता है। राम बारम्बार अपने तीखे बाणों से रावण का शीश काटते हैं किन्तु हर बार उसके धड़ पर नया शीश उग आता जाता है। देवराज इन्द्र यह विचित्र स्थिति देखकर कहते हैं कि प्रभु राम रावण के वक्ष पर बाण क्यों नहीं चलाते। इसपर भगवान ब्रह्मा गूढ़ रहस्य बताते हैं कि राम कभी रावण के हृदय को लक्ष्य करके बाण नहीं चलायेंगे क्योंकि वे जानते हैं कि रावण के हृदय में सीता का वास है, सीता के हृदय में राम का वास है और राम के हृदय में पूरी सृष्टि का वास है। इस अवस्था में यदि रावण के हृदय में बाण मारा गया तो उसके साथ सीता, स्वयं राम और पूरी सृष्टि का विनाश हो जायेगा। उधर राम की निरन्तर विफलता देखकर विभीषण उनके पास पहुँचते हैं और बताते हैं कि भगवान ब्रह्मा के वरदान से रावण की नाभि में अमृत है। राम अग्निबाण का संधान कर रावण की नाभि को भेदते हैं और उसका अमृत सुखा देते हैं। सारथि मातलि कहता है कि देवताओे ने रावण के विनाश का जो समय बताया था, वह आ चुका है। अब राम ब्रह्मास्त्र का प्रयोग कर रावण का अन्त करें। राम रावण पर ब्रह्मास्त्र चलाते हैं। रावण धरती पर आ गिरता है। प्राण छोड़ते समय पहली बार वह अपने मुख से राम को श्रीराम कहकर पुकराता है। तीनों लोक राम की जय जयकार करते हैं।

#tilak #navratri #dussehra #ravanvadh #katha #dussehravishesh #dussehrakatha

snippet.title: Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai | Ab Kaisa Hoga Abhira Ka Safar?
snippet.description:
Aankhon mein sapne lekar aap se milne aa rahi hai Akshara ki beti Abhira. Lekin uske swabhaav ko lekar uski Maa ko hai badi chinta. Ab kaisa hoga Abhira ka safar? 

Jaanne ke liye dekhiye, naye daur ki nayi kahani, #YehRishtaKyaKehlataHai mein, 6 November se, raat 9:30 baje, StarPlus aur kabhi bhi Disney+ Hotstar par.

snippet.title: B Praak - Mal Mal | Sonal Chauhan | Siddharth Gupta | Jaani | Amanninder Singh | Desi Melodies
snippet.description:
‘Mal Mal’, a gem from B Praak's debut album 'Zohrajabeen', is an evocative piece that delves into the profound depths of love and longing. It is the 5th video release from the album, showcasing the collaborative genius of B Praak, Jaani, and team Desi Melodies again. 

The lyrics, penned by Jaani, tell a beautiful story of true love and commitment. When you listen, B Praak's heartfelt voice makes you feel every emotion. The visual narrative, directed by the talented Amanninder Singh, seamlessly intertwines with the lyrical depth, and actors Sonal Chauhan and Siddharthh Gupta breathe life into the song's heartfelt narrative. Together, they create a moving portrayal of love that's both deep and divine, capturing the essence of fleeting moments and the unbreakable bond shared between two souls.

Listen to B Praak's 'Mal Mal' and all the hits from "Zohrajabeen" - http://www.umgindia.lnk.to/Zohrajabeen

Happy Dussehra And Happy Diwali To All 

Happy Vijayadashami Guy's....Vijayadashami, also known as Dussehra, Dasara or Dashain, is a major Hindu festival celebrated at the end of Navaratri every year in the Indian subcontinent.
In Ramayana, on this day, Lord Ram killed Ravana in Lanka and brought back his wife Sita. Hence, the people of his kingdom lighted diyas to celebrate his victory, the victory of good over evil. And thus, began the festival of Dussehra or Vijaya Dashmi.

Thanks For Watching Have Fun. Happy Diwali In Advance.

snippet.title: #Mega156 Pooja Ceremony | Megastar Chiranjeevi | Vassishta | MM Keeravani | UV Creations
snippet.description:
Mega 156 Pooja Ceremony on UV Creations. Megastar Chiranjeevi's 156th movie / Mega 156 2023 latest movie is directed by Vassishta. Music by MM Keeravani. Produced by UV Creations. 

#Mega156Begins #Chiranjeevi #MegastarChiranjeevi #Vassishta #MMKeeravani #UVCreations 

While Megastar Chiranjeevi along with his wife Smt Surekha handed over the script to the makers to begin the proceedings, Allu Aravind switched on the camera and Raghavendra Rao sounded the clapboard. The event was also attended by VV Vinayak, Maruthi and others.

Cast: Megastar Chiranjeevi

Technical Crew:
Writer & Director: Vassishta
Producers: Vikram, Vamsi, Pramod

snippet.title: NEW! Barsatein - Mausam Pyar Ka - Ep 77 | 24 Oct 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SET India: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 77: Reyansh's Decision
 -----------------------------------------------------------------
Reyansh asks Aradhana whether or not she loves him or not. Aradhana blames her for toxicity and says that she doesn't wants him in her life. Reyansh then agrees to get engage with Kimaya.  What will she do now? Will the engagement ceremony go smoothly? or any major twist waiting for Aradhana? What will happen now? Watch the episode to learn more. 

Show Name: Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka
Cast: Shivangi Joshi, Kushal Tandon
Episode: 77
Director: Atif Khan
Producer: Ekta Kapoor

#barsateinmausampyaarka #setindia #बरसातेंमौसमप्यारका #kushaltandon #shivangijoshi 

About Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Kaa:
------------------------------------------------------------
A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. While united in their passion for honest and ground-breaking journalism, their contrasting characters immediately put them at loggerheads. What will happen when she starts falling in love with him despite the red flags? 'Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka' stars Shivangi Joshi and Kushal Tandon in lead roles.
